end

% Final output of averageWeightedERP is (12 x 1): (1-4 = NLL, NRL, NLR, NRR), (5-8 = N-1_LL, N-1_RL, N-1_LR, N-1_RR), (9-12 = N-2_LL, N-2_RL, N-2_LR, N-2_RR)

